Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Christmas, and Alistair Cooke meets a computer
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yldz2
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 30 Dec 1993
A 1940s style flight to Vermont brings Alistair Cooke to his family and a computer which has swallowed several libraries, a few archives and already knows all about him.